Open the Ubuntu terminal and run the following commands to update the package list and upgrade installed packages:
bash
Copy code
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
->  sudo apt update
->  sudo apt upgrade
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Install the dependencies required for Ansible:
bash
Copy code
->  sudo apt install -y software-properties-common
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add Ansible Repository:
Add the Ansible repository to your system:
Copy code
->  sudo apt-add-repository --yes --update ppa:ansible/ansible
Install Ansible:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install Ansible using the following command:
Copy code
->  sudo apt install -y ansible
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Verify Installation:
After the installation is complete, you can verify the Ansible version:
Copy code
->  ansible --version
This should display information about the installed Ansible version.
